{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:24:32.209033+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Now I have a complete picture of the project. Let me give you an honest answer.\n\n---\n\n## Important: This Is Not a Flutter Web Project\n\nThe `web/` sub-project in this repository is an **AngularDart** progressive web app, not a Flutter web app. It uses the standalone **Dart SDK**, the **`webdev`** tool, and **`pub`** — not Flutter at all. The Flutter project lives in `mobile/` and only targets Android/iOS.\n\nAdditionally, `webdev build` outputs to **`web/build/`**, not `build/web/`. There is no build path that produces `build/web/` from this project.\n\n---\n\n## Shell Commands (Based on the README and CI Script)\n\n### Prerequisite: rename the TMDB config stub (required or the project won't compile)\n\n```bash\ncd core/lib/src && mv tmdb_config.dart.sample tmdb_config.dart && cd ../../..\n```\n\n### (a) Install web tooling\n\nThe README directs you to install the **standalone Dart SDK** (not Flutter's bundled Dart) and then:\n\n```bash\npub global activate webdev\n```\n\n### (b) Fetch dependencies\n\n```bash\ncd core && pub get && cd ..\ncd web && pub get && cd ..\n```\n\n(The `mobile/` directory is not needed for a web build.)\n\n### (c) Produce a release web build\n\n```bash\ncd web && webdev build --release\n```\n\nThis outputs compiled assets to **`web/build/`** (not `build/web/`).\n\n---\n\n### Caveats\n\n1. **Flutter web tooling** (`flutter build web`) does **not** apply here. The Flutter app in `mobile/` has no `web/` platform directory and targets Flutter 1.0, which predates Flutter web support.\n2. If you genuinely need a Flutter-web output at `build/web/`, this project would need significant migration work — the web app would need to be rewritten as a Flutter web app rather than its current AngularDart form.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 1193, "prompt_tokens": 11847, "t